videos.description: John Wolford keeps it himself and walks in untouched for touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wolford strolls in for games first TD

videos.description: Dontae Strickland gets a nice block on the edge, and explodes up the sideline for a 43-yard TD.  The Orange tie the game 7-7.
videos.headline: Syracuse responds with Strickland rushing TD

videos.description: RB Matt Colburn takes the hand-off and rushes it in for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest regains lead with rush TD

videos.description: Moe Neal finds a hole in the defense and bursts up the middle for a 47-yard gain.
videos.headline: Orange RB Neal makes a big play

videos.description: Zack Mahoney hits Ravian Pierce in stride for a 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Mahoney-Pierce connection ties game

videos.description: John Wolford throws a nice pass to Cam Serigne and he does the rest, scoring a 31-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest scores on 3rd straight possession

videos.description: Zach Mahoney throws a jump ball and Ervin Phillips snatches the ball away from the defender for a 26-yard catch.
videos.headline: Orange's Phillips makes tough catch for big gain

videos.description: Zack Mahoney hands it off to FB Chris Elmore who  barrels into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Syracuse rush TD ties high-scoring game

videos.description: Zach Mahoney lobs it up to Steve Ishmael who fights through contact to make a 30-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Syracuse takes its first lead with Ishmael TD

videos.description: Punt returner Alex Bachman tries to make the fair catch but his teammate Ja'Sir Taylor runs into him and the ball hits Bachman. Syracuse would recover the ball.
videos.headline: Wake Forest special teams makes costly turnover

videos.description: Zack Mahoney fakes the defense with a play-action read and finds Ravian Pierce for a 18-yard touchdown to extend the Orange lead to 38-21.
videos.headline: Syracuse extends lead with 2nd Mahoney-Pierce TD

videos.description: John Wolford rushes for a 9-yard touchdown to close the gap for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wolford TD run cuts into lead

videos.description: John Wolford fakes the handoff and finds Cam Serigne for the 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford connects with Serigne for Wake Forest TD

videos.description: Wake Forest's Mike Weaver's extra point is blocked and returned by Syracuse for two point.
videos.headline: Syracuse blocks returns blocked extra point for two

videos.description: On fourth down, John Wolford fakes the handoff and runs it 29 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford's TD run gives Wake Forest the lead

videos.description: John Wolford finds Cam Serigne for his third touchdown pass of the game. Wolford also had three rushing touchdowns and six overall scores in the game.
videos.headline: Wolford's 6th TD extends Wake Forest's lead
